Sue-Allen Tait (14) was last seen on Friday morning when she left for school. Susan Tait, Sue-Allen’s mother, told the Middelburg Observer that Sue-Allen attends W H de Klerk School in eMalahleni. The family resides in Mineralia, and Sue-Allen takes the bus to school each day. Sue-Allen told her mother that she would be visiting a friend on Friday after school, but would have returned home, “I have tried tracking her cell phone via an App that I use, but her phone must be turned off.” Susan is not certain where the friend she visited lives and cannot contact them. Sue-Allen has a tall and thin build. She has blue eyes and strawberry blonde hair and was last seen wearing her school uniform. Anyone with any information on Sue-Allen’s whereabouts is urged to please contact Susan on 076 714 0439.